scene.message:
Nanjo: Honestly, so many{nl}
detours. At this rate, the{nl}
sun'll set before the{nl}
hospital exam is over.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Behind the highway,{nl}
that's straight north,{nl}
right?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: To think there's{nl}
another tree like the one{nl}
in the infirmary...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: In the woods behind{nl}
the highway, I saw a{nl}
beautiful tree.{waitkey}{clearbox}It looks just like the one{nl}
in the infirmary.{waitkey}{clearbox}A strange tree — looking at{nl}
it puts you at ease.{waitkey}{ret}
